<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { title: 'web-obsidian · your knowledge vault in the browser' }) %>
</head>
<body class="landing-page">
  <header class="landing-nav">
    <a class="landing-brand" href="/">web-obsidian</a>
    <nav class="landing-nav-actions">
      <select class="lang-select" data-lang-switch aria-label="Language" data-i18n-attr="aria-label:lang_switch">
        <option value="en">EN</option>
        <option value="de">DE</option>
      </select>
      <a class="btn-ghost" href="/login" data-i18n="nav_signin">Sign in</a>
      <% if (typeof allowRegistration !== 'undefined' && allowRegistration) { %>
        <a class="btn-primary btn-inline" href="/register" data-i18n="nav_create">Create account</a>
      <% } %>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="landing-main">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1 data-i18n="hero_title">Your knowledge vault, in the browser.</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead" data-i18n="hero_lead">
        web-obsidian is an open-source, privacy-first knowledge vault you reach from any
        browser. Take notes, organize nested folders, sketch with Excalidraw and read PDFs &mdash;
        all online, with nothing to install. Your vault is encrypted at rest with AES-256.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn-primary btn-inline" href="/login" data-i18n="hero_open">Open your vault</a>
        <% if (typeof allowRegistration !== 'undefined' && allowRegistration) { %>
          <a class="btn-ghost" href="/register" data-i18n="hero_create_free">Create a free account</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="landing-section">
      <h2 data-i18n="diff_title">How it differs from Obsidian</h2>
      <p class="section-lead" data-i18n="diff_lead">
        The original Obsidian is a desktop app that keeps your notes offline on each device
        and relies on a separate sync service to keep them in step. web-obsidian flips that
        around: your vault lives online and you simply log in.
      </p>
      <div class="compare-grid">
        <div class="compare-card">
          <h3 data-i18n="card_nosync_h">Nothing to sync</h3>
          <p data-i18n="card_nosync_p">
            There is no sync to set up or pay for. Your notes are always in one place &mdash;
            log in from a laptop, PC or phone and pick up exactly where you left off.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare-card">
          <h3 data-i18n="card_browser_h">Browser-native</h3>
          <p data-i18n="card_browser_p">
            Built for the cloud and the browser instead of an offline desktop install. Open a
            tab on any device and your full vault is there.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare-card">
          <h3 data-i18n="card_secure_h">Account-based &amp; secure</h3>
          <p data-i18n="card_secure_p">
            Access is protected by your account with optional two-factor authentication (2FA).
            Privacy comes first &mdash; no tracking, no analytics.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare-card">
          <h3 data-i18n="card_enc_h">Encrypted at rest</h3>
          <p data-i18n="card_enc_p">
            Your notes, drawings and files are encrypted on the server with AES-256-GCM before
            they touch disk or object storage, so the stored data is unreadable on its own.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare-card">
          <h3 data-i18n="card_oss_h">Open source</h3>
          <p data-i18n="card_oss_p">
            The full source code is public. Use the hosted version or self-host it yourself
            from the published container image.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="landing-section">
      <h2 data-i18n="features_title">Features</h2>
      <p class="section-lead" data-i18n="features_lead">
        All the everyday building blocks of the original offline Obsidian &mdash; available
        online.
      </p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_notes">Markdown notes with live preview</span></li>
        <li><i class="bi bi-folder2-open"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_folders">Nested folders to organize your vault</span></li>
        <li><i class="bi bi-diagram-3"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_links">Wiki-style links between notes</span></li>
        <li><i class="bi bi-pencil"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_excalidraw">Excalidraw drawing integration</span></li>
        <li><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-pdf"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_pdf">Built-in PDF viewer</span></li>
        <li><i class="bi bi-paperclip"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_attach">Attachments &amp; file uploads</span></li>
        <li><i class="bi bi-search"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_search">Full-text search across your vault</span></li>
        <li><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-down"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_export">Export your whole vault as a zip</span></li>
        <li><i class="bi bi-shield-lock"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_2fa">Two-factor authentication (2FA)</span></li>
        <li><i class="bi bi-lock"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_enc">AES-256 encryption at rest</span></li>
        <li><i class="bi bi-moon-stars"></i> <span data-i18n="feat_themes">Light &amp; dark themes</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="landing-cta">
      <h2 data-i18n="cta_title">Ready to start?</h2>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn-primary btn-inline" href="/login" data-i18n="nav_signin">Sign in</a>
        <% if (typeof allowRegistration !== 'undefined' && allowRegistration) { %>
          <a class="btn-ghost" href="/register" data-i18n="nav_create">Create account</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
